These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, italian, french, indian
1. the italian is in an odd position##4
2. the indian is between the nigerian and the italian##2
3. the indian is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | nigerian | indian | italian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, blueberry, pepper, cranberry
1. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
2. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | blueberry | pineapple | cranberry | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, scientific, disaster, comedy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
2. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching scientific movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy | disaster | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, parkour, badminton, climbing
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is badminton##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | parkour | golf | climbing | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball, weightlifting, soccer
1. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | soccer | swimming | weightlifting | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, argentine, italian, spanish
1. the argentine is on the far right##1
2. the argentine is on the left or right of the spanish##3
3. the italian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | italian | indian | spanish | argentine |

