.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, basketball, baseball, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
4. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | baseball | badminton | swimming | basketball |

