.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, pumpkin, broccoli, corn
1. the person eating pumpkin is the person eating pumpkin##1
2. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
3. the person eating broccoli is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating lettuce is in an even position##4
5. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | broccoli | corn | pumpkin | lettuce |

